You shall speak to him

48:12.056 --> 48:15.595
And put the words in his mouth

48:15.810 --> 48:18.974
And I will be with your mouth

48:19.105 --> 48:20.437
And with his mouth

48:20.523 --> 48:21.639
Keep going.

48:21.732 --> 48:25.021
